race.comment: BERN WEST BOLTER (1) goes very well over this trip including three wins. Recorded a 4 length win (22.55) in a Novice race last time at this track. Has the ability and should feature. ZULU YALLAH (3) has a strong record this trip including four wins from four starts. Scored by 6 lengths last time (22.22) in a Grade 5/6 over 400m at this track. Looks well placed here and among the chances. CATCH THE FEELS (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from three tries. Scored by 6 lengths last time (22.38) in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Looks well placed here and among the chances. GEORDIE LAD (6) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.
